---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Dwizzy Infra" description="Read the privacy policy for Dwizzy Infra to understand how we collect, use, and protect your information.">
	<main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-14 lg:py-20 lg:max-w-5xl">
		<div class="mb-10 text-center">
			<h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-black">Privacy Policy</h1>
			<p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">Last updated: April 2, 2026</p>
		</div>

		<div class="space-y-8 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
			<section>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black mb-3">1. Information We Collect</h2>
				<p>
					We may collect personal information that you share with us through forms, calls, or email,
					such as your name, phone number, email address, company details, and project requirements.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black mb-3">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
				<p>
					Your information is used to respond to inquiries, provide project estimates, improve our
					services, and communicate updates related to your request.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black mb-3">3. Data Sharing</h2>
				<p>
					We do not sell personal data. We may share information with trusted service providers only
					when required to operate our business or fulfill services, and only under appropriate
					confidentiality safeguards.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black mb-3">4. Cookies and Analytics</h2>
				<p>
					This website may use cookies and analytics tools to understand visitor behavior and improve
					site performance. You can control cookie usage through your browser settings.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black mb-3">5. Data Security</h2>
				<p>
					We follow commercially reasonable security practices to protect your data. However, no
					internet transmission or electronic storage method is completely secure.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black mb-3">6. Your Rights</h2>
				<p>
					You may request access, correction, or deletion of your personal information by contacting us
					at <a href="mailto:info@dwizzyinfra.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">info@dwizzyinfra.com</a>.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-black mb-3">7. Contact</h2>
				<p>
					For any privacy-related questions, reach us at
					<a href="mailto:info@dwizzyinfra.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">info@dwizzyinfra.com</a>
					or call <a href="tel:+919217762100" class="text-primary hover:underline">+91 9217762100</a>.
				</p>
			</section>
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>
